<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content" 
    >

<LinearLayout
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="@android:color/holo_blue_light"
    android:orientation="vertical" >

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView1"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="49dp"
        android:text="1. They Move on. They don&apos;t waste time feeling sorry for themselves."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView2"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="59dp"
        android:text="2. They keep control. They don&apos;t give away their power."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView3"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="55dp"
        android:text="3. They embrace change. They welcome challenges."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView4"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="82dp"
        android:text="4. They stay happy. They don&apos;t complain. They don&apos;t waste energy on things they can&apos;t control."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView5"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="81dp"
        android:text="5.They are kind, fair, and unafraid to speak up. They don&apos;t worry about pleasing other people."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView6"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="72dp"
        android:text="6. They are willing to take calculated risks. They weigh the risks and benefits before taking action."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView7"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="52dp"
        android:text="7. They invest their energy in the present. They don&apos;t dwell on the past."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView8"
        android:layout_width="320dp"
        android:layout_height="77dp"
        android:text="8. They accept full responsibility for their past behavior. They don&apos;t make the same mistake over and over."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView9"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="57dp"
        android:text="9. They celebrate other people&apos;s success. They resent that success."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView10"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="76dp"
        android:text="10. They are willing to fail. They don&apos;t give up after failing. They see every failure as a chance to improve."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView11"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="52dp"
        android:text="11. They enjoy their time alone. They don&apos;t fear being alone."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView12"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="77dp"
        android:text="12. They are prepared to work and succeed on their own merits. They don&apos;t feel the world owes them anything."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView13"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="54dp"
        android:text="13. They have staying power. They don&apos;t expect immediate results."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView14"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="56dp"
        android:text="14. They evaluate their core beliefs and modify as needed."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView15"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="78dp"
        android:text="15. They expend their mental energy wisely. They don&apos;t spend time on unproductive thoughts."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView16"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="75dp"
        android:text="16. They think productively. They replace negative thoughts with productive thoughts."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView17"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="75dp"
        android:text="17. They tolerate discomfort. They accept their feelings without being controlled by them."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
    
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView18"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="77dp"
        android:text="18. They reflect on their progress every day. They take time to consider what they&apos;ve achieved and where they are going."
        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium" />
</LinearLayout>

</ScrollView>
